history.text: Hello, today I would like to introduce to you the animated film Zootopia. Have you seen this movie before?
I have not! Could you tell me about the main character?
The main character is Judy Hopps a little rabbit from the small rural town of Bunnyburrow. She moves to the utopian town of Zootopia to fulfill her dreams of becoming a police officer.
Are there any other important characters?
There is a sly fox named Nick Wilde, who cons Judy on the first day as a parking officer. Which she was assigned because her boss Chief Bogo doesn't think a rabbit can be a cop.
What animal is Chief Bogo?
He is an African buffalo
Okay! What makes this movie worth watching?
There is also a little sheep who is the assistant mayor of Zootopia
Critics have nothing but praise for this animated film, which is in the words of one critic "funny, smart, and thought-provoking."
How long is this movie?
This movie should be around an hour and twenty. It also has an excellent rating on IMDB and rotten tomatoes
What is the name of the sheep assistant mayor?
her name is Jenny Slate
Her voice is played by Jenny Slate and the sheep's name is Dawn Bellwether
Who voices the main character Judy Hopps?
Judy Hopps is voiced by Ginnifer Goodwin
Who voices the fox Nick Wilde?
Jason Bateman is the voice of Nick WIlde
Are there any bad guys in Zootopia?
The story is basically about Judy and Nick on the trail of a lost otter named Otterton, which leads them to uncovers some hidden crimes from mob bosses to someone causing animals to go "savage"
Would you call Zootopia a family movie?
For sure, it is a family comedy that you can enjoy with kids of all ages.
Who directed Zootopia?
